Paper: hep-th/9305132

Date: 1993-05-25

Title: Symmetries of the Chern-Simons Theory in the Axial Gauge

Authors: A. Brandhuber, S. Emery, M. Langer, O. Piguet, M. Schweda and S.P.

SorellaComments: 16 pages, report UGVA-DPT 1993/05-817, TUW 93-10

Journal-ref: Helv. Phys. Acta 66 (1993) 551-566

The Green functions of the Chern-Simons theory quantized in the axial gaugeare shown to be calculable as the unique, exact solution of the Ward identitieswhich express the invariance of the theory under the topological supersymmetryof Delduc, Gieres and Sorella.